#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.167"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.167:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.167:0.2"
msgid "17. Jāṇussoṇivagga "
msgstr "17. With Jāṇussoṇī "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.167:0.3"
msgid "167. Brāhmaṇapaccorohaṇīsutta "
msgstr "167. The Brahmin Ceremony of Descent "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.167:1.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhāto navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivattho allakusamuṭṭhiṃ ādāya bhagavato avidūre ekamantaṃ ṭhito hoti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time it was the sabbath. The brahmin Jāṇussoṇi had bathed his head and dressed in a new pair of linen robes. Holding a handful of fresh grass, he stood to one side not far from the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.250, sc2
msgctxt "an10.167:2.1"
msgid "Addasā kho bhagavā jāṇussoṇiṃ brāhmaṇaṃ tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhātaṃ navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivatthaṃ allakusamuṭṭhiṃ ādāya ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ. "
msgstr "The Buddha saw him, "

msgctxt "an10.167:2.2"
msgid "Disvāna jāṇussoṇiṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "and said, "

msgctxt "an10.167:2.3"
msgid "“kiṃ nu tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhāto navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivattho allakusamuṭṭhiṃ ādāya ekamantaṃ ṭhito? "
msgstr "“Brahmin, why have you bathed your head and dressed in a new pair of linen robes? Why are you standing to one side holding a handful of fresh grass? "

msgctxt "an10.167:2.4"
msgid "Kiṃ nvajja brāhmaṇakulassā”ti? "
msgstr "What’s going on today with the brahmin clan?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.167:2.5"
msgid "“Paccorohaṇī, bho gotama, ajja brāhmaṇakulassā”ti. "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, today is the ceremony of descent for the brahmin clan.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.167:3.1"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana, brāhmaṇa, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“But how do the brahmins observe the ceremony of descent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.167:3.2"
msgid "“Idha, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhātā navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivatthā allena gomayena pathaviṃ opuñjitvā haritehi kusehi pattharitvā antarā ca velaṃ antarā ca agyāgāraṃ seyyaṃ kappenti. "
msgstr "“Well, Master Gotama, on the sabbath the brahmins bathe their heads and dress in a new pair of linen robes. They make a heap of fresh cow dung and spread it with green grass. Then they make their beds between the boundary and the fire chamber. "

msgctxt "an10.167:3.3"
msgid "Te taṃ rattiṃ tikkhattuṃ paccuṭṭhāya pañjalikā aggiṃ namassanti: "
msgstr "That night they rise three times and worship the fire with joined palms: "

msgctxt "an10.167:3.4"
msgid "‘paccorohāma bhavantaṃ, paccorohāma bhavantan’ti. "
msgstr "‘We descend, lord! We descend, lord!’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:3.5"
msgid "Bahukena ca sappitelanavanītena aggiṃ santappenti. "
msgstr "And they serve the fire with abundant ghee, oil, and butter. "

msgctxt "an10.167:3.6"
msgid "Tassā ca rattiyā accayena paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena brāhmaṇe santappenti. "
msgstr "And when the night has passed they serve the brahmins with a variety of delicious foods. "

msgctxt "an10.167:3.7"
msgid "Evaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how the brahmins observe the ceremony of descent.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.167:4.1"
msgid "“Aññathā kho, brāhmaṇa, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī hoti, aññathā ca pana ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "“The ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is quite different from that observed in the training of the noble one.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.167:4.2"
msgid "“Yathā kathaṃ pana, bho gotama, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hoti? "
msgstr "“But Master Gotama, how is the ceremony of descent observed in the training of the noble one? "

msgctxt "an10.167:4.3"
msgid "Sādhu me bhavaṃ gotamo tathā dhammaṃ desetu yathā ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "Master Gotama, please teach me this.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.167:5.1"
msgid "“Tena hi, brāhmaṇa, suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“Well then, brahmin, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.167:5.2"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bho”ti kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavato paccassosi. "
msgstr "“Yes sir,” Jāṇussoṇi replied. "

msgctxt "an10.167:5.3"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.167:6.1"
msgid "“Idha, brāhmaṇa, ariyasāvako iti paṭisañcikkhati: "
msgstr "“It’s when a noble disciple reflects: "

msgctxt "an10.167:6.2"
msgid "‘pāṇātipātassa kho pāpako vipāko diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Killing living creatures has a bad result in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:6.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya pāṇātipātaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up killing living creatures, "

msgctxt "an10.167:6.4"
msgid "pāṇātipātā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from killing living creatures. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.167:7.1"
msgid "… ‘Adinnādānassa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Stealing has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:7.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:7.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya adinnādānaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up stealing, "

msgctxt "an10.167:7.4"
msgid "adinnādānā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from stealing. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.167:8.1"
msgid "… ‘Kāmesumicchācārassa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Sexual misconduct has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:8.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:8.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya kāmesumicchācāraṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up sexual misconduct, "

msgctxt "an10.167:8.4"
msgid "kāmesumicchācārā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from sexual misconduct. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.251, sc9
msgctxt "an10.167:9.1"
msgid "… ‘Musāvādassa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Lying has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:9.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:9.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya musāvādaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up lying, "

msgctxt "an10.167:9.4"
msgid "musāvādā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from lying. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.167:10.1"
msgid "… ‘Pisuṇāya vācāya kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Divisive speech has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:10.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:10.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya pisuṇaṃ vācaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up divisive speech, "

msgctxt "an10.167:10.4"
msgid "pisuṇāya vācāya paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from divisive speech. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an10.167:11.1"
msgid "… ‘Pharusāya vācāya kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Harsh speech has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:11.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:11.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya pharusaṃ vācaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up harsh speech, "

msgctxt "an10.167:11.4"
msgid "pharusāya vācāya paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from harsh speech. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an10.167:12.1"
msgid "… ‘Samphappalāpassa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Talking nonsense has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:12.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:12.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya samphappalāpaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up talking nonsense, "

msgctxt "an10.167:12.4"
msgid "samphappalāpā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from talking nonsense. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "an10.167:13.1"
msgid "… ‘Abhijjhāya kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Covetousness has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:13.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:13.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya abhijjhaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up covetousness, "

msgctxt "an10.167:13.4"
msgid "abhijjhāya paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from covetousness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "an10.167:14.1"
msgid "… ‘Byāpādassa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "… ‘Ill will has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:14.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:14.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya byāpādaṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up ill will, "

msgctxt "an10.167:14.4"
msgid "byāpādā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from ill will. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "an10.167:15.1"
msgid "… ‘Micchādiṭṭhiyā kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "‘Wrong view has a bad result "

msgctxt "an10.167:15.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe ceva dhamme abhisamparāyañcā’ti. "
msgstr "in the present life and in lives to come.’ "

msgctxt "an10.167:15.3"
msgid "So iti paṭisaṅkhāya micchādiṭṭhiṃ pajahati; "
msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up wrong view, "

msgctxt "an10.167:15.4"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhiyā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from wrong view. "

msgctxt "an10.167:15.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the ceremony of descent in the training of the noble one.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "an10.167:16.1"
msgid "“Aññathā kho, bho gotama, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī hoti, aññathā ca pana ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hoti. "
msgstr "“The ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is quite different from that observed in the training of the noble one. "

msgctxt "an10.167:16.2"
msgid "Imissā, bho gotama, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇiyā brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī kalaṃ nāgghati soḷasiṃ. "
msgstr "And, Master Gotama, the ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is not worth a sixteenth part of the ceremony of descent observed in the training of the noble one. "

msgctxt "an10.167:16.3"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama, excellent! … "

msgctxt "an10.167:16.4"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.167:16.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

